data.description: This stunning house with 5 or 4 bd, (office can be 5th bd if Next Gen is desired) and 4 1/2 bath, boasts modern design with high-end finishes and attention to detail throughout.  Elegant  spiral staircase and beautiful wood floors wow guests at the foyer and throughout the common areas of the home. The gourmet kitchen features high end stainless steel appliances, sleek countertops, farm sink, designer lighting and a large center island, which is open to dining featuring a fireplace, perfect for entertaining guests. The living room has soaring ceilings, offering lots of natural light. Three of the  bedrooms have en suite bath. The master suite is a true oasis, with a spa-like bathroom with a soaking tub, dual vanities & walk-in shower.  Relax in the private backyard, with fire pit and tree-lined easement, with no backyard neighbors!  Media room included: screen, receiver and projector!
